Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:04.48,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.82,0:23:10.15,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I want to be by your side more than anyone else
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.53,0:23:15.24,ED English,,0000,0000,0000,,Let’s go take a walk in chains of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:37.01,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\bord6\shad3\fs70\c&H5D01E2&\3c&HFCFDFC&\pos(640,530)}The Silver {\c&H71140C&\3c&HFBFBFB&}Advent Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.52,0:02:37.01,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(700,0)\shad1\fs70\be1\c&H5D01E2&\3c&HFCFDFC&\pos(640,530)}The Silver {\c&H71140C&\3c&HFBFBFB&}Advent Festival
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.00,0:23:40.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\b1\fs39\pos(200,175)\c&HF0EFEC&}Next Time
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.81,0:23:40.02,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\shad4\b1\fs46\pos(640,445)\c&HEDEFEE&}The Farewell Wedding Ceremony
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.43,0:00:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the Silver Advent Festival is your New Year's festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.82,0:00:18.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the middle of war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.14,0:00:21.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do the people in the city of South Goth not have any pride,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.75,0:00:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,welcoming their enemy and all?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.68,0:00:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did the Albion forces not protect their people, but they also ran away with the town's food supply, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.65,0:00:31.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Tristain forces gave food to the people in their stead,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.25,0:00:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's only natural for them to be welcomed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.71,0:00:38.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you only capable of thinking like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.26,0:00:40.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plebeians are plebeians, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.59,0:00:42.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.08,0:00:46.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well yeah, I'm different from aristocrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.03,0:00:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I prefer festivals to war.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.50,0:00:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, then go enjoy yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.49,0:00:55.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go see the Princess by myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.24,0:00:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.61,0:00:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need a dog following me!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.00,0:01:01.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, where's Saito-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito is...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.21,0:02:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've given him a task, so I'll hear the mission in his stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.72,0:02:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There was something that I wanted to ask Saito-san, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.21,0:02:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other day, we recovered Saito-san's vehicle from the mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.14,0:02:57.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Zero", was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.97,0:03:00.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can it be operated right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.59,0:03:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.19,0:03:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's an order, we'll do something about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you know, per Albion's proposal, we'll be in a truce during the Silver Advent Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.25,0:03:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you never know. They might attempt a surprise attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.54,0:03:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, we'd like you to fly to the\Ncapital, Londinium, and spy on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.11,0:03:22.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.08,0:03:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will be the ones breaking the truce if we use a dragon from our Air Force.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the other hand, you two can say that you're\Nstudents if you were to get caught by any chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.58,0:03:35.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The results from the last mission were pitiful,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:38.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm sure you two can do fine if it's just scouting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.22,0:03:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We will not fail you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.15,0:03:44.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't be rash.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.45,0:03:46.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.99,0:03:54.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is hard without Colbert-sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.61,0:04:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Julio, I have a favour to ask of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.25,0:04:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.79,0:04:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't ask anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.97,0:04:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a favour for my beautiful Louise, I'll fulfil it no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.73,0:04:24.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.76,0:04:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you are a dragon knight in the Musketeer Force but haven't joined Tristain's military, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.00,0:04:33.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't since I'm a flamen from Romalia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.17,0:04:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's he doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.14,0:04:39.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.50,0:04:43.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise, what are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.45,0:04:45.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Going on a date, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.03,0:04:46.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Would you not bother us?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.28,0:04:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.22,0:04:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:51.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're off on a secret mission by order of the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.50,0:04:53.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, get on my Zero!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't fly right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I can fix it in a rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.90,0:05:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you don't want to help out with the war effort, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.38,0:05:03.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need a familiar who only complains!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.96,0:05:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go wherever you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.47,0:05:06.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.44,0:05:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.76,0:05:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us, Saito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.81,0:05:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Louise!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:29.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With what?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.74,0:05:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He was hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.09,0:05:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.06,0:05:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He won't understand me at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.21,0:05:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn her.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.12,0:05:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn Louise.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.70,0:05:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why won't she understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito... san?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Siesta?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.45,0:05:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined I'd see you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.87,0:05:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here in Albion?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The school's closed for a while,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and I have an uncle who's starting a business here,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.29,0:06:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so I had him bring me with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, your uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.97,0:06:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.31,0:06:15.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.56,0:06:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me M-Master Scarron is your uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.71,0:06:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.61,0:06:27.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you calling an uncle, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.07,0:06:30.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, young lady.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.91,0:06:34.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And what's this? Saito and Siesta were friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.56,0:06:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, well, we know each other from the Magic Academy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Then the boy Siesta said she wanted to look for in Albion,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.30,0:06:46.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the great person whom she loves unrequitedly, but wants to get no matter what,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.71,0:06:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is Saito?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.18,0:06:52.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.38,0:06:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,hey-hey-hey-hey-hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:54.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.51,0:06:56.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito, you playboy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.49,0:06:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Two-tim-ing Louise-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.73,0:07:01.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A love triangle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.54,0:07:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.59,0:07:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, Miss Vallière isn't with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.76,0:07:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.66,0:07:18.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't look like they're preparing to march out or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.45,0:07:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.29,0:07:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surrender, you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.56,0:07:27.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you guys intend to betray your country?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, we're only saying that we should consider it a possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we focus on defence, we should be able to withstand them for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.68,0:07:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we lack sufficient force to attack with.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.23,0:07:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's no matter how much force we have.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.90,0:07:44.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was able to get some results, but there is no\Nlonger any merit in using this country further.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.65,0:07:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You asked me to take part in this\Nmission for Saito-kun's sake, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.38,0:07:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For Saito's sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't force a pacifist to go to war\Nand put him in a dangerous situation, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.10,0:08:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about that dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.99,0:08:03.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.57,0:08:07.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want Saito-kun to be safe even if you were to die in war.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You care about him so much, but he just doesn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.54,0:08:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you're angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:14.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oops, looks like chatting time is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.71,0:08:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Azuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what do you plan on doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.87,0:08:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll bite your tongue if you talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.14,0:08:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Breath!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:42.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,End of mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.73,0:08:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go back, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.86,0:08:48.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:51.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How kind of you to worry about their well-being.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.34,0:08:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's Saito-kun's influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.22,0:08:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.55,0:09:03.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.26,0:09:10.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But what a surprise that {\i1}you{\i0} are the boy that Siesta loves!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.41,0:09:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.59,0:09:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel bad for Louise, but I think I have to root for my cousin.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:18.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cousin?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.97,0:09:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.40,0:09:24.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're alike, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.47,0:09:28.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in our family has big breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.74,0:09:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,See? Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.75,0:09:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that muscle?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.45,0:09:37.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito! Isn't that Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.62,0:09:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guiche!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.99,0:09:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.84,0:09:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.39,0:09:47.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a White Spirit Medal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not much, but I was distinguished on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.10,0:09:57.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Poitier gave it to me in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.86,0:09:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:03.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To an aristocrat, there is no greater honour!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.84,0:10:10.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.77,0:10:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, even when your master's back and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.73,0:10:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.55,0:10:19.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah, what?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.76,0:10:21.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.19,0:10:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Wasn't he with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.63,0:10:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. You acted coldly to him again, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.97,0:10:31.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then Partner went away with a bitter face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.17,0:10:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't being cold to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.00,0:10:33.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.94,0:10:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.31,0:10:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He shouldn't talk back to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.00,0:10:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He should just follow the orders I give him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.49,0:10:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He says he loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.05,0:10:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's got nothing to do with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.13,0:10:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.51,0:10:50.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner gave up on going home and joined the war to follow you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:54.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Though he doesn't want to get involved in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you think that is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.24,0:11:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he's my familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.15,0:11:00.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he loves you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.00,0:11:04.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you ever responded to his feelings, even once?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While he devotes himself to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.66,0:11:12.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't whipping the only thing you do to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, where's Louise?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.52,0:11:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.34,0:11:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.93,0:11:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and I thought I'd show her the medal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.91,0:11:41.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you go call her, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.52,0:11:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know... Deep down, I'm really grateful to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But he's my familiar and a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.76,0:11:56.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without my having to tell him so every time,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he should understand how I feel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:02.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking for the impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.29,0:12:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He seems to be lacking in relationship experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.43,0:12:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And if the war continues, and if I were to die in it, he would never understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.69,0:12:19.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why. Instead of keeping it inside, why don't you tell him exactly how you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.93,0:12:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And make a solid bond with him while you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bond?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.34,0:12:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do I do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.17,0:12:31.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is what you say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.74,0:12:33.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"I love you! I love you, Saito!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.08,0:12:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Please! Marry me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.38,0:12:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Marry?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.81,0:12:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Make me your bride, make love to me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Pamper me!"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.39,0:12:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.12,0:12:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think an aristocrat could say "l-love" and "m-marry me" and "m-make love to me"...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.37,0:12:56.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...to a familiar?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.31,0:12:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.71,0:13:03.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner says that in the world he comes from, there are no plebeians nor aristocrats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.08,0:13:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he doesn't understand your standpoint.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.79,0:13:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know! Why don't you two swap positions for a day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:10.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swap positions?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.00,0:13:12.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll become Saito's familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.15,0:13:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.22,0:13:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, that's a great idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.53,0:13:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will be able to come to a good understanding if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.42,0:13:24.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understanding?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.94,0:13:29.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-ha. It's that room, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.20,0:13:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Will Saito really be happy with this outfit?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.66,0:13:35.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.34,0:13:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Partner's simple-minded, so he'll be emotionally touched to know how much you love him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.26,0:13:43.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, he's back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.82,0:13:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're... y-you're my master tonight! Meow, meow!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.82,0:14:02.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.03,0:14:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Louise, you were adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.05,0:14:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, yup, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:18.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're on the floor in that outfit, you'll get lots of customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.79,0:14:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.98,0:14:25.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez... I wondered what you were doing while I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.44,0:14:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth, Partner,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she was...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:31.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-So you know, it wasn't for you, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who was it for?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.75,0:14:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.32,0:14:38.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,J-Julio!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Delflinger said that if I wear the cat outfit and say,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.27,0:14:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"You're my master for the night, meow",
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.07,0:14:46.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could make Julio fall for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.20,0:14:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.06,0:14:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.77,0:14:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.81,0:14:53.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.30,0:14:56.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.00,0:14:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.80,0:15:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's superior to you in looks, brains{\i1} and{\i0} swordsmanship.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.25,0:15:06.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His dragon-controlling ability was godly.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.75,0:15:08.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to him, you're a pinworm to his lion,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.63,0:15:09.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,fly to his phoenix,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.81,0:15:11.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,water flea to his swan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.97,0:15:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then enjoy your time with Julio!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.98,0:15:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, looks like everyone's here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.64,0:15:20.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Julio...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.19,0:15:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm going back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.16,0:15:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:29.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-kun, did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.37,0:15:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I'd know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-pyon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.22,0:15:35.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Siesta?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, who's cuter, Miss Vallière or me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.42,0:15:43.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.75,0:15:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Who, you ask...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.71,0:15:52.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this outfit?! Trying to mock me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.69,0:15:55.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A maid dares to make fun of {\i1}me{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.68,0:16:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I only want Saito-san to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, stop it, both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.23,0:16:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep it up, Siesta!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.02,0:16:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn this!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.92,0:16:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magistrate Sheffield, can we really use\Nthe secret measure for repelling the enemy here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.09,0:16:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A third of South Gotha's water supply comes from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.55,0:16:45.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.91,0:16:47.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ring of Andvari.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.27,0:16:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It controls both the living and the dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.46,0:17:00.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have the war continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.70,0:17:03.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who exactly are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.76,0:17:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General. Do the rest as we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.24,0:17:12.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I leave Albion in your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.34,0:17:13.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Magistrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.92,0:17:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fairy, you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.26,0:17:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean a cute girl like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No! A real fairy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.52,0:17:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, a fairy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.73,0:17:25.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really saw one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.91,0:17:31.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It happened when we encountered an\Nenemy while marching from Lowscythe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.47,0:17:35.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I noticed, I was surrounded by enemies in the mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.86,0:17:37.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.92,0:17:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was surely inflicted a fatal wound.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:42.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.98,0:17:44.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I woke up again, {split here}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.86,0:17:47.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my body didn't have a single scar.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.30,0:17:50.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, fairy-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.47,0:17:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.98,0:17:56.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans are likely to see strange dreams when they're faced with death.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.25,0:17:57.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't a dream!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.03,0:18:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Either way, I'm glad you're alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:05.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's frightening to die in war, in an unknown land.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.85,0:18:09.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, no, I'm an aristocrat.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.60,0:18:11.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not afraid of dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.07,0:18:15.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can die any time I'm asked to for the sake of honour.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But if possible, I'd like to be more recognised, so I can die with another medal on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.74,0:18:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.53,0:18:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What did you call me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.79,0:18:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it, but you came back after nearly dying, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.31,0:18:34.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then cherish that life!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.77,0:18:39.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dying for the sake of honour? That's garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.35,0:18:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito! Apologise to Guiche!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.57,0:18:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.35,0:18:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Honour is more important than life to aristocrats!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.65,0:18:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many times do I have to tell you until you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.54,0:18:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You, too! Why won't you understand me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.97,0:18:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything ends when you die no matter how many medals you get!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.10,0:18:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need medals.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.42,0:18:58.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's important is loyalty to the Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.25,0:19:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need anyone to recognise me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.47,0:19:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only need the Princess to understand me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.64,0:19:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is my honour.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.66,0:19:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I would gladly give my life if it's for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.82,0:19:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suit yourself, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.26,0:19:19.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:23.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:25.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About the cat outfit...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't for Julio, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about Julio!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:30.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.68,0:19:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.33,0:19:36.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My true rival for Louise is... the Princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.71,0:19:38.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.39,0:19:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.09,0:19:41.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.30,0:19:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you angry at me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.74,0:19:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm troubling you, following you all the way to Albion, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.26,0:19:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.53,0:19:51.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.60,0:19:52.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm freezing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.89,0:19:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.17,0:19:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I drank too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.61,0:20:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Henrietta's men are your enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill your enemies.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.28,0:20:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill your enemies!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.41,0:20:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, do you feel warmer?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:15.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.32,0:20:20.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.31,0:20:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't cold at all to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.30,0:20:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just that... I wanted to feel your warmth.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.72,0:20:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.11,0:20:29.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stupid Saito.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.06,0:20:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When will he understand me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.39,0:20:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want a stronger bond, not just one between master and familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.51,0:20:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.39,0:20:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your Highness, there's a revolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.03,0:20:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Some of our own men are assaulting our soldiers!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.74,0:20:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What ridiculous things are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.23,0:20:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:01.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,General Poitier!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.74,0:21:07.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something strange is happening outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.62,0:21:09.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.33,0:21:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll return to Miss Vallière's side, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.45,0:21:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.35,0:21:21.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please take this with you, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.04,0:21:24.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a sleeping potion.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.78,0:21:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Miss Vallière tries to make you do something dangerous,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.80,0:21:31.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,make her take this, and run away while she's asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.67,0:21:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Siesta...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.22,0:21:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It may be natural for aristocrats to die for the Princess,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.52,0:21:41.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I can't stand having you get caught up in it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.72,0:21:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.28,0:21:48.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.44,0:21:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's Saito?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.14,0:21:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Saito!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.17,0:23:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.41,0:23:28.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is goodbye,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:31.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so... I'll marry you!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.36,0:23:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Zero no Tsukaima. Futatsuki no Kishi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.33,0:23:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Farewell Wedding Ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:38.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to meet me again next week, then sit tightly and wait!
